  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"page phb\" id=\"p85\"><p>Finally at 17th level, the darkness has raised you on your journey towards becoming a Shinobi, making you the angel of darkness. You can attack with your <em><strong>Dedication to Justice</strong></em> feature even when an attack would miss you. Additionally, when you land a critical hit on a creature, the creature gains 1 rank of Fear against you for 1 minute. Finally, for every hostile creature within 60 feet of you, you gain a +1 to unarmed attack and Taijutsu critical threat range. (Max. +3)</p></div><div class=\"page phb\" id=\"p86\"><div class=\"columnWrapper\"><h3 id=\"new-hunter-s-exploit-echolocation\"></h3></div></div>",
